snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
From Director James Cameron, watch the trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash.
Experience the film only in theaters December 19.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Britain Dalton, Trinity Bliss, Jack Champion, Bailey Bass and Kate Winslet.

——
ABOUT AVATAR
Director: James Cameron
Cast: Sam Worthington, Zoe Saldaña, Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang
Films: Avatar & Avatar: The Way of Water 

Visit our website: https://www.avatar.com/

snippet.title: Beéle - Quédate (Letra)
snippet.description:
Quédate - Beéle (Letra/Lyrics) #Quédate #Beele
Este que está aquí a ti no te quiere dejar, este que está aquí también se deja llevar.

Escucha el vídeo oficial: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0ElD2qJ5ZoU

🎧 Sigue a Beéle:
Spotify: https://open.spotify.com/artist/4O4bsz9qtjFi8oqtoP38vE
YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/@h.yeneey.12
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/beelemusic/
TikTok: https://www.tiktok.com/@beeleoficial

📢 No olvides suscribirte al canal para más lyrics de tus canciones favoritas 🔔

Letra de la canción:
¿Cómo le explico al corazón que quieres irte?
Si tienes dudas, mami, no te estoy mintiendo
Mira mis ojos mientras mi alma se desviste
Los que miras justo cuando me estoy viniendo
Cómo quisiera que estuvieras aquí
Me sintieras a mí al ladito tuyo
Pa' que veas que yo no puedo fingir
Y me puedo morir por los besos tuyos
Cómo quisiera que estuvieras aquí
Me sintieras a mí al ladito tuyo
Pa' que veas que yo no puedo fingir
Y me puedo morir por los besos tuyos

Ven quédate, quédate
No puedo estar sin ti
Quédate, quédate
Oh-oh, no puedo estar sin ti
Oh, no-no-no
Oh, no-no-no
Quédate
No puedo estar sin ti

Este que está aquí a ti no te quiere dejar
Este que está aquí también se deja llevar
Estamo' destinados a juntos celebrar la Navidad
Esto nunca tuvo sentido, fuimos en contra de la Ley Universal
Qué visaje, cule' viaje
Dime cómo evitamos las señales
A veces yo quisiera que no pare
Pero esto me va a matar
Quiero ver qué responde, no me tira ni: "Hola"
Y yo aquí con cule' bartola
Pensando en toda' las noche' que estuvimos a solas
Y no le parábamos bolas
Chingando con un feeling, somos Reyes de las Olas
Estoy frente a tu alma, porfa, ma', déjame entrar
Permíteme que entienda' que no existe nadie más
Y si me quedo contigo es porque tú eres la mondá

Ven quédate (quédate), quédate (quédate)
No puedo estar sin ti (sin ti)
Quédate, quédate
No, no puedo estar sin ti
Oh, no-no-no
Oh, no-no-no
Quédate (alright, alright)
No puedo estar sin ti

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Der Tiger | Official Trailer
snippet.description:
"We reap what we sow" - Watch the trailer for #DerTigerMovie now, and see it in select German theaters September 18!
 
Eastern Front, 1943: The five-man crew of a German Tiger tank is sent on a secret mission far behind the heavily contested front line. As they journey eastward, the soldiers not only find themselves deeper in enemy territory but must also face their own fears and inner demons. Stimulated by Wehrmacht methamphetamine, their mission increasingly becomes a journey into the heart of darkness.
 

„Wir ernten was wir säen“ - #DerTigerMovie ab 18. September in ausgewählten deutschen Kinos!
 
Ostfront, 1943: Die fünfköpfige Besatzung eines deutschen Tiger-Panzers wird auf eine geheime Mission weit hinter die hart umkämpfte Frontlinie geschickt. Auf ihrem Weg nach Osten geraten die Soldaten nicht nur immer tiefer in feindliches Gebiet, sondern müssen sich auch ihren eigenen Ängsten und Abgründen stellen. Aufgeputscht durch das Methamphetamin der Wehrmacht, wird ihre Mission immer mehr zu einer Reise in das Herz der Finsternis.


About Amazon MGM Studios: Amazon MGM (Metro Goldwyn Mayer) is a leading entertainment company focused on the production and global distribution of film and television content across all platforms. The company owns one of the world’s deepest libraries of premium film and television content as well as the premium pay television network MGM+, which is available throughout the U.S. via cable, satellite, telco and digital distributors.  In addition, Amazon MGM has investments in numerous other television channels, digital platforms and interactive ventures and is producing premium short-form content for distribution.

Stimulated by Wehrmacht methamphetamine, their mission increasingly becomes a journey into the heart of darkness.
 

„Wir ernten was wir säen“ - #DerTigerMovie ab 18. September in ausgewählten deutschen Kinos!
 
Ostfront, 1943: Die fünfköpfige Besatzung eines deutschen Tiger-Panzers wird auf eine geheime Mission weit hinter die hart umkämpfte Frontlinie geschickt. Auf ihrem Weg nach Osten geraten die Soldaten nicht nur immer tiefer in feindliches Gebiet, sondern müssen sich auch ihren eigenen Ängsten und Abgründen stellen. Aufgeputscht durch das Methamphetamin der Wehrmacht, wird ihre Mission immer mehr zu einer Reise in das Herz der Finsternis.

ja.title: アバター ファイア＆アッシュ 予告編 2025：炎を操る達人
ja.description:
アバター 炎と灰 2025年版予告編。ジェームズ・キャメロン監督の『アバター3』、新たな火の部族の悪役解説、ファイアベンダー、ヴァランの悪役、ジェイク・サリー、ネイティリ、キリ、クォリッチ、ローク、スパイダー、そして『アバター4』と『アバター5』の予告編 ► https://bit.ly/AwesomeSubscribe
ファンタスティック・フォー ポストクレジットシーン https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bS0k5LEl3-w&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
ファンタスティック・フォー レビューhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dxErxB5E2Ks&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
スーパーマン：フラッシュ＆ジャスティス・ソサエティのイースターエッグ https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GeMPr-40pMc&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=2&pp=gAQBiAQB
スーパーマン：すべてのイースターエッグと参考資料 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QgoyaMHk2RQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=2&pp=gAQBiAQB0gcJCdgJAYcqIYzv
スーパーマン：ポストクレジットシーン https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7NVbJdIHKTA&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
アベンジャーズ ドゥームズデイ ファーストルック https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2E1gEtPrzj0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
スパイダーマン：ブラン・ニュー・デイ ファーストルック https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lCmqSbnYfo0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
アベンジャーズ ドゥームズデイ 予告編https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bQfK5VSwLHQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
緊急！素晴らしい新着動画 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

2025年公開の『アバター 炎と灰』の最新予告編、ジェームズ・キャメロン監督の『アバター3』、新たな火の国「ファイアベンダー族」について解説。アバター4と5の映画ティーザー、ジェイクとネイティリの子供たちがストーリーを支配している理由、クォリッチの復帰、ジェイクとクォリッチの再戦、最終決戦シーン、キリの能力とパワー、スター・ウォーズにおけるアナキン・スカイウォーカーへの言及。

現在、アバター映画は4と5の2本が計画されています。ジェームズ・キャメロン監督は、アニメ版アバター映画のアンソロジー形式を制作すると発言しています。今後、アバター映画やテレビ番組のスピンオフ、続編がさらに制作される可能性もあります。

コミコンウィークエンドなので、マーベル、DCコミックスなどからたくさんの予告編が公開されています。できる限り動画を制作したいと思っています！アベンジャーズ：ドゥームズデイ予告編、アベンジャーズ：6シークレット・ウォーズ予告編、スーパーマン、そしてファンタスティック・フォーの動画も近日公開予定です。

ブラックパンサー：ワカンダ・フォーエバーのエピソード動画は、全エピソードが公開される金曜日から投稿を開始します。アバター・ファイア＆アッシュの映像がもっと公開されたら、もっと動画を撮ります！

स्पाइडर-मैन ब्रांड न्यू डे का पहला दृश्य https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lCmqSbnYfo0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे का ट्रेलर https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bQfK5VSwLHQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
आपातकालीन शानदार नए वीडियो https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

नए अवतार फायर एंड ऐश ट्रेलर 2025 को कवर करते हुए। जेम्स कैमरून अवतार 3 मूवी, नए फायर नेशन फायरबेंडर ट्राइब की व्याख्या। अवतार 4 और अवतार 5 मूवी के टीज़र, जेक और नेयतिरी के बच्चे कहानी पर क्यों हावी हो रहे हैं, क्वारिच की वापसी, जेक क्वारिच का रीमैच, अंतिम युद्ध के दृश्य, किरी की शक्तियाँ और क्षमताएँ, स्टार वार्स अनाकिन स्काईवॉकर के संदर्भ।

फिलहाल दो और अवतार फ़िल्में, अवतार 4 और अवतार 5, बनाने की योजना है। जेम्स कैमरून ने अवतार फ़िल्मों के संकलन शैली में एनिमेटेड अवतार फ़िल्म बनाने की बात कही है। और भविष्य में अवतार फ़िल्मों या टीवी शो के और भी स्पिनऑफ़ या सीक्वल आ सकते हैं।

चूँकि यह कॉमिक कॉन वीकेंड है, मार्वल, डीसी और अन्य जगहों से ढेरों ट्रेलर आ रहे हैं, इसलिए मैं हर संभव वीडियो बनाने की कोशिश करूँगा! एवेंजर्स डूम्सडे ट्रेलर, एवेंजर्स 6 सीक्रेट वॉर्स ट्रेलर, सुपरमैन और फैंटास्टिक फ़ोर के और भी वीडियो जल्द ही।

मेरे ब्लैक पैंथर वकांडा फॉरएवर एपिसोड के वीडियो शुक्रवार को पोस्ट होने शुरू हो जाएँगे जब वे सभी एपिसोड रिलीज़ करेंगे। और जब वे और फुटेज रिलीज़ करेंगे, तो मैं अवतार फ़ायर और ऐश के और भी वीडियो बनाऊँगा!

ko.description:
아바타 파이어 앤 애쉬 예고편 2025. 제임스 카메론 감독 아바타 3 영화, 새로운 불 부족 악당 설명, 파이어벤더스, 바랑 악당, 제이크 설리, 네이티리, 키리, 콰리치, 로악, 스파이더 & 아바타 4 및 아바타 5 영화 티저 ► https://bit.ly/AwesomeSubscribe
판타스틱 4 크레딧 후 장면 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bS0k5LEl3-w&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
판타스틱 4 리뷰 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dxErxB5E2Ks&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
슈퍼맨 플래시 & 저스티스 소사이어티 이스터 에그 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GeMPr-40pMc&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=2&pp=gAQBiAQB
슈퍼맨 모든 이스터 에그와 참고 자료 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QgoyaMHk2RQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=2&pp=gAQBiAQB0gcJCdgJAYcqIYzv
슈퍼맨 포스트 크레딧 장면 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=7NVbJdIHKTA&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwCLH9RIm-7ui56ameRYmdQ&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
어벤져스: 둠스데이 첫 공개 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2E1gEtPrzj0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
스파이더맨: 새로운 시작 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lCmqSbnYfo0&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
어벤져스: 둠스데이 예고편 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bQfK5VSwLHQ&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczwWT3yd94Xc6n-ooI85uV_u&index=1&pp=gAQBiAQB
긴급 상황, 멋진 새 영상 https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=FeOfhzu7ZdY&list=PLOIeYdZ3QczxQXxyV_2D8kuEs_QsuQIyJ&index=7

새로운 아바타 파이어 앤 애쉬 예고편(2025년). 제임스 카메론 감독의 아바타 3 영화, 새로운 불의 나라 파이어벤더 부족에 대한 설명. 아바타 4와 아바타 5 영화 티저, 제이크와 네이티리 아이들이 스토리라인을 장악하는 이유, 쿼리치의 귀환, 제이크 쿼리치의 재대결, 마지막 전투 장면, 키리의 힘과 능력, 스타워즈 아나킨 스카이워커 관련 정보.

현재 아바타 영화는 아바타 4와 아바타 5, 두 편이 더 계획되어 있습니다. 제임스 카메론 감독은 애니메이션 아바타 영화 앤솔로지 스타일로 제작할 것이라고 언급했습니다. 앞으로 아바타 영화나 TV 프로그램 스핀오프 또는 후속작이 더 많이 나올 수도 있습니다.

코믹콘 주말이라 마블, DC 등 다양한 곳에서 예고편이 많이 올라오니, 가능한 모든 영상들을 제작해 보려고 합니다! 어벤져스 둠즈데이 예고편, 어벤져스 6 시크릿 워즈 예고편, 슈퍼맨, 그리고 더 많은 판타스틱 포 영상들이 곧 공개될 예정입니다.

블랙 팬서 와칸다 포에버 에피소드 영상은 모든 에피소드가 공개되는 금요일에 업로드될 예정입니다. 그리고 아바타 파이어와 애쉬 영상도 영상이 더 많이 공개되면 더 많이 올릴 예정입니다!

snippet.title: AVATAR: FIRE AND ASH TRAILER REACTION!! Avatar 3 | James Cameron
snippet.description:
NA'VI VS NA' VI?! Use code *50REELREJECTS* to get 50% OFF plus free shipping on your first Factor box at https://bit.ly/4ftNIcS!
OHHHH WE COOKIN'!! The brand‑new Avatar 3: Fire and Ash trailer dropped during The Fantastic Four screenings and we lost it in the theater! Greg Alba & John Humphrey break down every jaw‑dropping moment from the teaser: intense battles between Jake Sully, Neytiri and the war‑like Ash People / Mangkwan clan led by Varang (Oona Chaplin), fire‑wielding Na’vi riding burning banshees, the haunting realization that the Ash People have rejected Eywa, internal Na’vi conflict and tragic grief over Neteyam’s death, Jake and Neytiri’s kids in peril—especially young Kiri (Sigourney Weaver) facing Varang’s threat—Spider’s shifting allegiances and Quaritch’s alliance with the Ash people—that shot of Captain Quaritch stepping into Ash territory with red war paint was chilling. We also catch glimpses of the peaceful Wind Traders in sky‑ships, returning faces like Sam Worthington’s Jake Sully, Zoe Saldaña’s Neytiri, Cliff Curtis as Tonowari, Kate Winslet as Ronal, Edie Falco’s General Ardmore, Stephen Lang’s Recombinant Quaritch, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, and newcomer David Thewlis as Peylak. This trailer teases family trauma, volcanic biomes, aerial banshee fights, love between Lo’ak and Tsireya, internal Na’vi civil war, the return of RDA forces and possible human off‑world implications beyond Pandora's atmosphere. Featuring themes of grief, vengeance, redemption, war, fire vs water, tribal division—you can feel the emotional punch and stakes going in deeper than ever. Avatar: Fire and Ash, directed by James Cameron, hits theaters December 19, 2025. Don't miss our full breakdown reaction—subscribe, hit the bell icon, and dive in with us! Cast and characters featured include: Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), Kiri (Sigourney Weaver), Colonel Quaritch (Stephen Lang), Tonowari (Cliff Curtis), Ronal (Kate Winslet), General Ardmore (Edie Falco), Parker Selfridge (Giovanni Ribisi), Dr. Norm Spellman (Joel David Moore), Mo’at (CCH Pounder), Lo’ak (Britain Dalton), Tsireya (Bailey Bass), Peylak (David Thewlis), Varang (Oona Chaplin), Dr. Ian Garvin (Jemaine Clement), and more. Pack your banshee, it’s going to be explosive!

snippet.title: Mario Paint - Super NES – Nintendo Classics
snippet.description:
Unlock the artist within!

snippet.title: IT: Welcome To Derry Comic-Con Trailer (2025) Bill Skarsgård,  Pennywise TV Show 4K
snippet.description:
🎈 IT: WELCOME TO DERRY – Comic-Con Trailer (2025) 🎈
Bill Skarsgård returns as the terrifying Pennywise in IT: Welcome to Derry, the highly anticipated prequel TV series to Stephen King’s IT. Premiering exclusively on Max (HBO), this new horror saga dives deep into the origins of evil in stunning 4K.

🩸 Series Overview:
Set decades before the events of IT, Welcome to Derry explores how the nightmare began. As sinister disappearances plague the small town of Derry, Maine, a group of kids uncover a malevolent presence lurking beneath the streets — the ancient evil that would become known as Pennywise the Dancing Clown.

🎬 Starring:
Bill Skarsgård as Pennywise
Taylour Paige
Jovan Adepo
James Remar
Chris Chalk
Madeleine Stowe

📺 Streaming on: Max (HBO)
📆 Release Date: Fall 2025
🎞️ Genre: Horror | Supernatural | Thriller | Drama

hi.description:
🎈 आईटी: वेलकम टू डेरी - कॉमिक-कॉन ट्रेलर (2025) 🎈
बिल स्कार्सगार्ड स्टीफन किंग की आईटी की बहुप्रतीक्षित प्रीक्वल टीवी सीरीज़ आईटी: वेलकम टू डेरी में डरावने पेनीवाइज़ के रूप में वापसी कर रहे हैं। मैक्स (एचबीओ) पर विशेष रूप से प्रीमियर होने वाली यह नई हॉरर गाथा शानदार 4K में बुराई की उत्पत्ति की गहराई में उतरती है।

🩸 सीरीज़ अवलोकन:
आईटी की घटनाओं से दशकों पहले की कहानी, वेलकम टू डेरी इस दुःस्वप्न की शुरुआत की पड़ताल करती है। मेन के छोटे से शहर डेरी में भयावह गायबियों के बीच, बच्चों का एक समूह सड़कों के नीचे छिपी एक दुष्ट उपस्थिति का पता लगाता है - वह प्राचीन बुराई जिसे बाद में पेनीवाइज़ द डांसिंग क्लाउन के नाम से जाना गया।

🎬 अभिनीत:
बिल स्कार्सगार्ड, पेनीवाइज़ के रूप में
टेलर पेज
जोवन एडेपो
जेम्स रेमर
क्रिस चाक
मेडेलीन स्टोव

📆 रिलीज़ तिथि: 2025 की शरद ऋतु
🎞️ शैली: हॉरर | अलौकिक | थ्रिलर | ड्रामा

हमारे सभी चैनल सदस्यों का बहुत-बहुत धन्यवाद!

hi.title: पोपेय द सेलर मैन (2026) - लाइव एक्शन ट्रेलर | जेसन स्टैथम, एम्मा स्टोन - कॉन्सेप्ट ट्रेलर
hi.description:
#popeyethesailorman #jasonstatham #emmastone

यह "POPEYE THE SAILOR MAN - लाइव एक्शन रीबूट | फैन-मेड कॉन्सेप्ट ट्रेलर" देखें

यह दिग्गज गुस्से से भरे मुक्कों और पालक के डिब्बे के साथ लौटता है।

इस बोल्ड लाइव-एक्शन फैन-मेड कॉन्सेप्ट ट्रेलर में, Popeye the Sailor Man को नई पीढ़ी के लिए नए सिरे से तैयार किया गया है। जेसन स्टैथम एक साहसी, मज़बूत दिल वाले नाविक में बदल जाते हैं, जबकि एम्मा स्टोन, प्रतिष्ठित ओलिव ऑयल में आकर्षण, बुद्धि और लचीलापन लाती हैं।

हास्य, दिलकश और रोमांचक एक्शन का मिश्रण, यह रीबूट पोपेय को भ्रष्टाचार से ग्रस्त एक आधुनिक दुनिया में फिर से पेश करता है, जहाँ एक मुक्का भी बदलाव ला सकता है—और सच्चा प्यार कभी पीछे नहीं हटता।

वह अंत तक मज़बूत है, और उसने अभी तक लड़ाई पूरी नहीं की है।

अस्वीकरण:
यह एक फैन-मेड कॉन्सेप्ट ट्रेलर है जिसे पूरी तरह से मनोरंजन के उद्देश्य से बनाया गया है। यह एक गैर-व्यावसायिक परियोजना है जिसका पैरामाउंट पिक्चर्स, किंग फीचर्स सिंडिकेट या किसी भी आधिकारिक पोपेय प्रोडक्शन से कोई संबंध नहीं है। पोपेय और संबंधित पात्रों के सभी अधिकार उनके संबंधित स्वामियों के पास हैं।

प्रशंसकों द्वारा बनाए गए ट्रेलरों के साथ-साथ, मैं मनोरंजन जगत से फ़िल्म समीक्षाएं, समाचार और अपडेट भी साझा करता/करती हूँ। कृपया सब्सक्राइब बटन ज़रूर दबाएँ और मेरे चैनल की सभी नवीनतम जानकारी से अपडेट रहें!

ko.title: 뽀빠이 세일러맨 (2026) - 실사 예고편 | 제이슨 스테이섬, 엠마 스톤 - 콘셉트 예고편
ko.description:
#popeyethesailorman #jasonstatham #emmastone

"뽀빠이 세일러맨 실사 리부트 | 팬 제작 컨셉 예고편"을 시청하세요.

전설이 분노의 주먹과 시금치 한 캔을 들고 돌아옵니다.

이 대담한 실사 팬 제작 컨셉 예고편에서 뽀빠이 세일러맨은 새로운 세대를 위해 새롭게 재탄생했습니다. 제이슨 스테이섬은 순전히 순수한 마음을 가진 투지 넘치고 강인한 선원으로 변신하고, 엠마 스톤은 상징적인 올리브 오일에게 매력, 재치, 그리고 회복력을 더합니다.

유머, 진심, 그리고 거친 바다 액션이 어우러진 이 리부트는 부패로 얼룩진 현대 사회에서 뽀빠이를 다시금 그려냅니다. 단 한 번의 펀치로도 변화를 만들 수 있고, 진정한 사랑은 결코 물러서지 않습니다.

그는 끝까지 강하며, 아직 싸움을 멈추지 않았습니다.

면책 조항:
본 예고편은 순수하게 오락 목적으로 제작된 팬 제작 컨셉 예고편입니다. 본 프로젝트는 파라마운트 픽처스, 킹 피처스 신디케이트 또는 공식 뽀빠이 제작사와는 아무런 관련이 없는 비상업적 프로젝트입니다. 뽀빠이와 관련 캐릭터에 대한 모든 권리는 해당 소유자에게 있습니다.

팬들이 직접 제작한 예고편 외에도 영화 리뷰, 뉴스, 엔터테인먼트 업계의 최신 소식을 공유합니다. 구독 버튼을 눌러 제 채널의 모든 최신 소식을 받아보세요!

snippet.title: How a 50,000-Hour Trio DOMINATES by ONLY RAIDING - Rust
snippet.description:
I hired Gorliac and Ledoo, two Rust specialists, to play a competitive clan server. Our original plans for the wipe were to contest these clans, but as a trio we realized our best way to stay ahead of the game was to do something a bit different. RAID... EVERYBODY.... With our combined ~50,000 hours, our skill and gamesense gave us the confidence we needed to survive. I hope you enjoy!

snippet.title: How FAST Can You KILL a KILLER? [Forsaken]
snippet.description:
Forsaken is a game where survivors work together to stay alive with a killer on the loose. But when you look at the numbers, what can you discover?

In this video, I looked deeper at the Forsaken roster to break down a typical misconception about Killing Forsaken Killers. This just might help someone doing a Forsaken Challenge or even Forsaken Trolling.

And don't forget to SUBSCRIBE! We're gonna make it to 200K together!

About Forsaken:
Forsaken is a game with ten survivor characters including Noob, Two Time, Guest 1337, Shedletsky, Elliot, Dusekkar, Builderman, Chance, 007n7, and Taph. There are currently FIVE killer characters as well: Jason, C00lkidd, 1x1x1x1, John Doe, and Noli.

#roblox #forsaken #challenge

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 13 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.

snippet.title: Destiny 2 will Die if Bungie doesn't fix this soon...
snippet.description:
Ranting about the current state of the Destiny 2 Leveling System. This is one of the Most Complained About subjects within the Destiny 2 Community after the Release of the Edge of Fate, and Bungie needs to improve this System ASAP, or Destiny 2 will be Dead. 
--FOLLOW ME ON TWITCH: www.twitch.tv/kackishd

--- My Twitter: https://twitter.com/RickKackis

New #destiny2 video, going over the current Destiny 2 Leveling System. If you want to level up fast with your gear score and reach the New Max Gear Score permanent band of 200 power, and eventually reach the new Max Gear Score (Max Level) of 450, you're in for an absolute slog! After the Edge of Fate Campaign on Legendary difficulty in the New Edge of Fate DLC, this will become extremely important! The New Edge of Fate DLC Launch is Here! We have the New Year of Prophecy and Season: Renewal (Season of Renewal) that have gone live! We have a New Edge of Fate Campaign, and Kepler, the new Edge of Fate Destination! There are many Kepler Secrets to uncover! We also have the New Sieve Activity! And we have Armor 3.0, Destiny 2 Stats Overhaul, and the New Destiny 2 Portal! All leading to the New Destiny 2: Renegades Star Wars DLC!
But today we're going over the massive problems with the Destiny 2 Leveling System! If you try to increase your Gear Score Fast, which will let you Level Up Fast with improved Score in the Portal and more Prime Engrams Drops, among other things, you have to farm the same activity for endless hours! Destiny 2 is dying and the Destiny 2 Player Count is not great, so this needs to be fixed asap!  #Destiny2News #Destiny2EdgeOfFate

What is Roblox? ROBLOX is an online virtual playground and workshop, where kids of all ages can safely interact, create, have fun, and learn. It’s unique in that practically everything on ROBLOX is designed and constructed by members of the community. ROBLOX is designed for 8 to 18 year olds, but it is open to people of all ages. Each player starts by choosing an avatar and giving it an identity. They can then explore ROBLOX — interacting with others by chatting, playing games, or collaborating on creative projects. Each player is also given their own piece of undeveloped real estate along with a virtual toolbox with which to design and build anything — be it a navigable skyscraper, a working helicopter, a giant pinball machine, a multiplayer “Capture the Flag” game or some other, yet-to-be-dreamed-up creation. There is no cost for this first plot of virtual land. By participating and by building cool stuff, ROBLOX members can earn specialty badges as well as ROBLOX dollars (“Robux”). In turn, they can shop the online catalog to purchase avatar clothing and accessories as well as premium building materials, interactive components, and working mechanisms.
